sequenceDiagram
    participant OP as Operator
    participant HMI as HMI
    participant PLC as PLC
    participant SEN as Sensors
    participant ACT as Diverter

    OP->>HMI: Press Start
    HMI->>PLC: CMD_StartAuto
    PLC->>PLC: Check permissives
    PLC->>SEN: Read infeed + class input
    SEN-->>PLC: Item detected + class/weight
    PLC->>PLC: Track item to sort position
    PLC->>ACT: Actuate diverter pulse
    ACT-->>PLC: Actuation complete
    PLC->>HMI: Update counters/status
    PLC->>HMI: Raise alarms if fault
